OL,3,CCoroner demands changes at GP surgery
OL,4,Cafter death of toddler
OL,6,FA coroner has written to a GP surgery
OL,7,Fover concerns about the case of a
OL,8,Ftoddler who later died with Strep A.
OL,10,FMichael Pemberton has filed a
OL,11,F'prevention of future deaths' report,
OL,12,Fafter presiding over an inquest
OL,13,Flooking into what happened to 22-month-
OL,14,Fold Hailey Thompson.
OL,16,FHailey's death was caused by sepsis
OL,17,Fand pneumonia, which was caused by
OL,18,FGroup A streptococcus, a bacterial
OL,19,Finfection otherwise known as Strep A.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
