OL,3,CCoroner demands changes at GP surgery
OL,4,Cafter death of toddler
OL,6,FIn the report, Mr Pemberton raised
OL,7,Fconcerns about how Ashton Medical
OL,8,FPractice dealt with a request for an
OL,9,Fappointment from Hailey's mother
OL,10,FIbolya Adam.
OL,12,FIt came after the toddler had an
OL,13,Fallergic reaction to antibiotics she
OL,14,Fwas taking for a suspected throat
OL,15,Finfection in the days before her
OL,16,Fdeath. The antibiotics were stopped a
OL,17,Ffew days after Hailey developed a rash.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
