OL,6,FMs Adam spoke to an administrative
OL,7,Fstaff member, known as "a care
OL,8,Fnavigator", who asked a pharmacist to
OL,9,Fcall her.
OL,11,FBut that pharmacist could not deal
OL,12,Fwith paediatric medication and sent a
OL,13,Fmessage explaining this, though it was
OL,14,F"not on the medical records system
OL,15,Fwhere an auditable trail would exist".
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@JO]vD@AOUwD@eO]
