OL,6,FMr Pemberton also raised concerns that
OL,7,Fthe care navigator did not have a
OL,8,F'clear pathway... or triage tool to
OL,9,Frecognise that a reported allergic
OL,10,Freaction to a medication may require
OL,11,Furgent consideration by a doctor to
OL,12,Fassess any risk of anaphylactic shock'.
OL,14,FMr Pemberton wrote: "The jury who
OL,15,Fheard the inquest found that there was
OL,16,Fa missed opportunity to review the
OL,17,Fantibiotics, which was not causative
OL,18,Fin this case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
