OL,4,Cafter death of toddler
OL,6,F"In my opinion, there is a risk that
OL,7,Fan urgent need for appropriate
OL,8,Fclinical referral may not occur in the
OL,9,Fabove circumstances."
OL,11,FMr Pemberton said: "During the course
OL,12,Fof the investigation my inquiries
OL,13,Frevealed matters giving rise to
OL,14,Fconcern.
OL,16,F"In my opinion there is a risk that
OL,17,Ffuture deaths could occur unless
OL,18,Faction is taken. In the circumstances
OL,19,Fit is my statutory duty to report to
OL,20,Fyou."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
