OL,6,FSSP Health's Andy Scaife said: "We are
OL,7,Fdeeply saddened at the death of one of
OL,8,Four patients. Our thoughts and
OL,9,Fheartfelt condolences are with
OL,10,FHailey's family and loved ones during
OL,11,Fthis difficult time.
OL,13,F"We have received the Regulation 28
OL,14,FReport from the Coroner but cannot
OL,15,Fcomment, in detail, at this time as we
OL,16,Fare still reviewing the report
OL,17,Ffindings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
