OL,6,F"We note that the concerns raised by
OL,7,Fthe Coroner relate to common practices
OL,8,Fwhich are in place across the vast
OL,9,Fmajority of doctors surgeries in the
OL,10,Fcountry and are not specific to the
OL,11,Fsurgery in this case. We also note
OL,12,Fthat the Coroner specifically states
OL,13,Fthat the concerns raised did not
OL,14,Fcontribute to this very sad death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
