OL,6,F"As is appropriate, we are currently
OL,7,Fconducting a thorough internal review
OL,8,Fto understand the exact circumstance,
OL,9,Fwhich will include a review of the
OL,10,Ffactual accuracy of certain aspects of
OL,11,Fthe report and the appropriateness of
OL,12,Fa Regulation 28 Report being raised in
OL,13,Fthis case. Once completed, our
OL,14,Fresponse will be shared with the
OL,15,FCoroner."
